  "method": [
    "Take a broad platter or sharp knife.",
    "In little plates, insert the eggplant spreads, spicy feta spreads, and",
    "potato spreads plates or spoons on your board directly.",
    "Organize the spreads around all of the other components so that the",
    "colors are nicely scattered.",
    "In order to do this, there is no wrong or right path. Only try to stop",
    "putting all the green vegetables next to each other.",
    "The same for orange. To each mix, add micro spoons so that your",
    "guests can quickly scatter each dip.",
    "Keep the rest of the baked goods (pita, bruschetta, grilled bread, and",
    "breadsticks), so they are not dry.",
    "Just before eating, warm pita bread and cut it into pieces!"
  ],
